### Simple Bank API
### Requires server running: go run .
### Default from .env: HOST=0.0.0.0, PORT=8080

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080

### ----------------------------------------
### Accounts
### ----------------------------------------

### Create account
# @name createAccount
POST {{baseUrl}}/accounts
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "owner": "alice",
  "currency": "USD"
}

###

### Get account by ID
# Replace 1 with an ID returned from create account
@id = 1
GET {{baseUrl}}/accounts/{{id}}

###

### List accounts
GET {{baseUrl}}/accounts?page_id=1&page_size=5
